 Did you know that we will meet 29.2 million people in our lifetime? 

215
00:14:40,699 --> 00:14:46,719
 When I think about it, meeting you at the age of 16 should be one of my few lucky moments in life. 

216
00:14:46,719 --> 00:14:50,719
 The first time I saw you, you were sitting on the grass and playing guitar. 

217
00:14:50,719 --> 00:14:54,799
